.fmbot help & command overview
Overview of all ServerSettings commands
Commands: .refreshmembers · i | Refreshes the cached member list that .fmbot has for your server. .configuration · ss | Shows server configuration for .fmbot .members · mb | view members in your server that have an .fmbot account .keepdata | Allows you to keep your server data when removing the bot from your server .servermode | Sets the forced .fm mode for the server. .serverreactions | Sets the automatic emoji reactions for the fm and featured command. .prefix | Changes the .fm prefix for your server. .toggleservercommand | Enables or disables a command server-wide .togglecommand | Enables or disables a command in a channel .cooldown | Sets a cooldown for the fm command in a channel. .addwebhook | Adds featured webhook to a channel. This will automatically post all .fmbot features to this channel. .testwebhook | Test the .fmbot webhook in your channel .fmbotactivitythreshold | Sets amount of days to filter out users for inactivity. Inactivity is counted by the last date that someone has used .fmbot .block | Block a user from appearing in server-wide commands and charts .unblock | Remove block from a user from appearing in server-wide commands .blockedusers | View all users that are blocked from appearing in server-wide commands .crownthreshold | Sets amount of plays before someone can earn a crown in your server .crownactivitythreshold | Sets amount of days to filter out users from earning crowns for inactivity. Inactivity is counted by the last date that someone has used .fmbot .crownblock | Block a user from gaining any crowns in your server .removeusercrowns | Removes crowns from a user .crownblockedusers | View all users that are blocked from earning crowns in your server .togglecrowns | Completely enables/disables crowns for your server. .killcrown · kcw | Removes all crowns from a specific artist for your server. .crownseeder | Automatically generates or updates all crowns for your server .killallcrowns | Removes all crowns from your server .killallseededcrowns | Removes all crowns seeded by the crownseeder command. All other manually claimed crowns will remain in place.
